h()` utility that:\n   - In development: resolves to project root's `.trellis/`\n   - In npm package: resolves to bundled template files\n\n5. **Build/Package Consideration**: The `package.json` likely needs updating to include `.trellis/` in the package. Currently templates are read at runtime via `fs.readFileSync`.\n\n6. **Backwards Compatibility**: The external API (exported template strings) should remain unchanged to avoid breaking configurators."}],"totalDurationMs":90109,"totalTokens":48332,"totalToolUseCount":26,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8012,"cache_read_input_tokens":40317,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":8012,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard"}}}
